summary: Okay, no. Do they really think that this is good? The event is literally in TWELVE DAYS. Who the fuck has money to buy plane...
body: Okay, no. Do they really think that this is good? The event is literally in TWELVE DAYS. Who the fuck has money to buy plane tickets and find a hotel in TWELVE DAYS? Like I get it, they tried their best but this is shit. This is not good, this is not what Brazil wanted. And we need to fucking acknowledge that they screwed up big time. Most of their Brazilian fans won’t be able to go. This is REALLY bad, they fucked up.

summary: It’s very comforting to know that Dan and Phil are at a point where they can naturally tell us stuff along the lines of “he ran...
body: It’s very comforting to know that Dan and Phil are at a point where they can naturally tell us stuff along the lines of “he ran into the room in his underwear.” Three years ago those words would have never left Phil’s mouth and I’m just so happy how much they’ve grown and how trusted their fan base is nowadays.
